{"tid":1488459,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「不割蓆，會檢討」喺抗爭必勝方程式","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:52:18.000Z","uid":52609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e222cef9e3ae12e8c5834c1c0c6ee91cae5f5a5","tid":1488459,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">「不割蓆」：團結所有手足，不論角色都企硬，核彈都唔割<br />\n「會檢討」：檢討，修正錯誤，不斷改善、進步</span></strong><br />\n兩樣野加埋先喺我地抗爭必勝方程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白後勤擔心前線，但大家檢討要Be Humble，唔好一嚟就鬼鬼聲，好傷前線心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下檢討簡略整合可能不完美，但會努力改善，繼續檢討改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">1. 一日應只有一個重點<br />\n2. 不合作運動要令市民得益：免費過紅隧、地鐵跳閘<br />\n3. 不主動捉鬼，捉到鬼後影相，放人，不打人不包圍<br />\n4. 不打記者，不打救護，不任意攻擊平民<br />\n4. 盡早開戰，入夜撤退<br />\n5. 要有行動目標，方便定進退<br />\n6. 前線決定下一步</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【戰略】</span></span></strong><br />\n621 624 圍稅局 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 阻礙市民到稅局難以爭取中立市民支持，「唔好意思」行動</span></strong><br />\n83 旺角再遊行<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 由塞紅隧變免費過紅隧</span></strong><br />\n85 三罷<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 一日應只有一個重點，全日衝突令三罷人數被冷處理</span></strong><br />\n813 機場<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 主動阻旅客失民心。不打記者。不打救護，不任意攻擊平民。不主動捉鬼，捉到鬼後影相、放人，不打人、不包圍</span></strong><br />\n813 - 816 塞地鐵 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 阻礙市民返工難以爭取中立市民支持，從善如流取消活動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【戰術】</span></span></strong><br />\n69 深夜衝立法會被圍捕抄牌<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong> ➤ 盡早開戰，入夜撤退</strong></span><br />\n612 瘋狂催淚彈，橡膠彈，布袋彈<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 前線Gear升級：豬嘴、頭盔、盾牌...</span></strong><br />\n621 衝夏愨道，圍狗總 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 不鳩佔道路，要有行動目標方可定進退，前線決定下一步</span></strong><br />\n71 立法會 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 一齊走！不破壞文物，不偷野 </span></strong><br />\n77 旺角<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 要有行動目標方可定進退。狗沸水戰術，包抄前離開</span></strong><br />\n714 沙田<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 要有行動目標方可定進退。制空權！救手足！ </span></strong><br />\n727 元朗<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 旗手制度出現，嘗試解決示威者去與留爭議 </span></strong><br />\n728 西環<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> ➤ 前線企疏啲令最前排可以走動／要反擊畜龍 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武為劍 和理為盾<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰  不捉鬼 不譴責<br />\nBe Water Be Humble<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f4b2481ce59bcc6d83c567ae053a4ca971987ba8","tid":1488459,"uid":34020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"37bc9f123c3e555a4d0ded43a2026af7afdb1b28","tid":1488459,"uid":15365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6549ffbf3516dbc45fb68c81c1426925fd75f3d8","tid":1488459,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思 麻煩大家幫手投票定個死線<br />\n大家既訴求唔可以不了了之</span></span><br />\n死線投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54e7fa89f8a02fa05f309659d732e13ed15f35fc","tid":1488459,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2489d13b52e7b7d83aa37d505daf593df60fd2","tid":1488459,"uid":413